we have an application that store the images
that our users upload.

when we want to store an image
we want to compress that image first (reduce the size)
we want to apply filter (images have a common look)
like black & white filter or high contrast filter
so we have "compressor" & "filter" field on ImageStorage class

problem1: violating single responsibility principle
          our ImageStorage class should store images!
          but now he do filter and compressing
          (if we implement the method instead simulating filtering and compressing
           our class will be so big!)


problem2: it is difficult to support new compressors or new filters
          if we want to add new filter, we should come back here
          and make change in different parts
          it will be so hard when our class be large!
